Name: SUBJECTIVE IMAGE QUALITY
Explanation: RATING OF THE EXCELLENCY OF AN IMAGERY BASED ON AN INDIVIDUALS PERCEPTION.

Name: IMAGE QUALITY, EXTENDED
Explanation: SPECIFIES THE IMAGE QUALITY BASED ON EITHER THE NATIONAL IMAGERY INTERPRETABILITY RATING SCALE (NIIRS), RADAR NATIONAL IMAGERY INTERPRETABILITY RATING SCALE (RNIIRS), OR MAGNIFIED IMAGERY RATING SCALE (MIIRS).

Name: SUBJECTIVE DETAIL
Explanation: REFLECTS THE ANALYST'S IMPRESSION OF THE QUALITY OF DETAIL THAT CAN BE GAINED FROM THE IMAGERY.
